{"tid":528201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食個飯都比廢老圍","createTime":"2018-01-13T13:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T14:21:39.000Z","uid":4575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec7bf9e24e6d893a68211a3181bbb3934fc89be","tid":528201,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:50:37.000Z","msg":"啱啱一條友係大家樂食飯，間野冇乜人坐2*4既長枱已經執好晒枱，同枱一邊有對情侶一人一煱。咁我坐一邊角一路食一路上連登，冇啦啦對面有人盆就走開，抬頭一望食完既，仲要一排3盆！我望下對原來係隔離枱班廢老坐低，順手張人地食完既盆放我E枱。想小佢地之際另一廢老又拿一盆繞過我背後想放我右手邊！我即屌佢話，屌你唔係諗住用食剩既野圍住我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話：好啦好啦⋯⋯好似我錯咁。最後我望住3盆野食飯，之後自己清返自己盆，其實隔多一張枱已經有收盆車<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/215034_10271f381754625e93024aa617c82974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F215034_10271f381754625e93024aa617c82974.jpg&h=3a188898&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6a8de11005c04f76a7828cb52a0d1190ba18192","tid":528201,"uid":150611,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0d532a560c0bdbc5910539a963edafdd215611c","tid":528201,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"比我唔忍，翻檯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f266076fb644ad0cde7470eac11f1bc50c2bd14","tid":528201,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:15:29.000Z","msg":"食大家樂都係on9"},{"pid":"21f136aaf44bd7fd49c38f004012163c2db84510","tid":528201,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"青衣撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337bfe2a9562d22e678d4538c8d3835fc2f300a7","tid":528201,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T14:21:39.000Z","msg":"咁你食完個盆咪放返去佢張枱度囉<br />\n<br />\nbtw 食完野又執埋枱，班廢老仲霸住張枱做乜？"}]}